        <item>
            <title>【評測】小米 Watch S4 開箱評測，佩戴舒服 + 功能齊全 + 電量不夠「長氣」+ 定價抵玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/mi-watchs4-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi-watchs4-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/mi-watchs4-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 03:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Watch S4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303865</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>除了兩款新耳機外，小米近日亦發佈了最新款的智能手錶 Watch S4，Edward 亦同樣試用了一段時間，現在就與大家分享一下使用體驗吧。</p><h2>小米 Watch S4 開箱直擊</h2><p>同樣地，為大家分享小米 Watch S4 這款全新智能手錶的使用體驗前，先讓 Edward 為大家帶來它的開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01931.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是小米最新推出的智能手錶 Watch S4 的包裝盒。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01933.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲從包裝已可看到，小米 Watch S4 支援藍牙 5.3 制式，是可以配對 iPhone 或 Android 手機使用的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01941.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打開包裝盒，就見到 Watch S4 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305164" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01944.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底層就放了説明書及 Watch S4 專屬的磁吸式 USB 充電線，開箱部分至此結束。</p><h2>設計平實走大眾路線</h2><p>今次小米推出的 Watch S4 智能手錶，設有黑、銀及特別的黑彩虹色設計，不過設計上無論哪種顏色，Watch S4 都是走偏向沉實風的大眾路線，不過話雖如此，但外觀看起來 Watch S4 還是十分不錯，很有一般傳統腕錶的感覺。另外 Watch S4 亦有不少不同質地的錶帶供用家選購，除了附送的氟橡膠錶帶，亦有尼龍或小牛皮物料選擇，顏色亦有橙、藍、白等，用來配襯服裝十分不錯。除了錶帶外，Watch S4 亦可替換錶圈，而購買錶帶時包裝內亦有對應相同風格的錶圈附送，用家可以與不同錶帶作一套風格裝上，或者可以自行 mix and match，同樣十分不錯，當中灰藍色雙時區的錶帶及錶圈設計，以灰、藍雙色各半以展示不同時區最為特別，設計亦最搶眼，亦是筆者個人最愛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305166" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01973.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Watch S4 錶身採用了金屬物料製造，感覺頗為硬淨，而筆者測試的是黑色錶身，設計風格較為平實。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01968.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錶冠頗為漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01970.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而下方就設有功能鍵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01983.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305170" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01985.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而 Watch S4 最特別的設計，就是連錶圈都可以替換。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305171" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01987.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲基本上只要將錶圈內側的橙色實心標誌，與錶盤上的橙色外框標誌對準再扭動錶圈，就可以將它裝上錶上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305172" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01958.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01956.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於錶帶方面，黑色版本附送的是氟橡膠錶帶，雖然是塑膠但感覺物料頗為親膚。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01964.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而錶帶同樣是可以替換的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01992.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錶盤的設計亦與傳統手錶十分相似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171-261x580.jpg" alt="" width="261" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171-261x580.jpg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_202504171.jpg 405w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 261px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當然，預設亦有不同設計的錶面供用家選用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01999.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02001.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲部分錶面更可讓用家自行設定顯示內容。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01993.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01994.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而按實熒幕就可以在不同錶面之間切換使用。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
