        <item>
            <title>滴滴推「經濟型」選項可以不叫的士，實試叫車比 Uber 平達 20%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=didi-vs-uber</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Apr 2025 12:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305306</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港滴滴出行靜靜地推出了一款全新「經濟型」私家車服務，可以不呼叫的士而呼叫經濟型私家車，進一步擴展本地業務版圖。新服務提供比預約的士更具吸引力的車費，與市場另一競爭者 Uber 相比，同一路線價格最多相差 20 港元。記者實測顯示，滴滴經濟型私家車在特定路線及時段展現出明顯價格優勢，預計此舉將重新激起香港網約車平台的競爭格局。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲滴滴新增「經濟型」車輛選項</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲在點經濟型車輛後，將叫「KayGo」品牌的私家車<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>滴滴出行自上週五起，開始分階段開放經濟型私家車服務予香港用戶。原本僅限網約的士的滴滴，現於 App 介面新增「經濟型」專區，乘客可透過簡單操作預約私家車，享用比的士更低的車費。根據平台資料，這類車輛由 KayGo 車隊提供，該公司正積極招攬本地私家車司機，擴展服務規模。滴滴方面預告，短期內會向所有香港用戶全面開放這項服務。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>價格方面，記者於非繁忙時段實測，由觀塘偉業街至旺角山東街，滴滴經濟型車費約為 HK$82，Uber 同時間、同路段普通車型則收費 HK$104，如享有折扣價則為 HK$92，比起滴滴「經濟型」叫車貴 10-18 元。而在滴滴叫的士的預計跳錶價則為 HK$89 元起。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲叫車由觀塘偉業街至旺角山東街，在記者叫車時段收費 HK$82.21，叫合作的士收費由 HK$89.05 起<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲同一時段呼叫 Uber, 未折扣前價格為 HK$104.48，如有折扣則為 HK$92.48<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_81712-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>但我們也發現 Uber 在長途車的價格反而會比滴滴「經濟型」選項便宜。例如由觀塘偉業街至觀塘型點商場 1 期，Uber 收費在折扣前只為 HK$321，而滴滴經濟型車輛則需要 HK$336。建議用戶在出發前，應自行比較滴滴及 Uber 兩款 App 的即時報價，以獲得最抵選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>以上價格只供參考，實際收費以各平台叫車當時的收費為準。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/">滴滴推「經濟型」選項可以不叫的士，實試叫車比 Uber 平達 20%</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
